snippet.textDisplay:
This is burned into my childhood memories. I played this game so much. Only problem, as a half-deaf child in a noisy arcade, I had no idea what the hell they were saying in this song. And since I was nearsighted, I kept misreading the labels.

I thought the game was "Lootoneyah." And would yell this at the top of my lungs during the triumphant chorus of this song before I started the game. Ahhh, childhood innocence.

LET'S GO AWAY
